{"tid":1863979,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【TVB推優惠未能阻止客戶流失　出糧每月燒1.3億 邁入最後倒數？】","createTime":"2020-02-05T11:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T15:13:21.000Z","uid":51701,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5df032bce243043e158d245710906e1cbb0201","tid":1863979,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=f95e8a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nCCTVB 網戰洗皮長期要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKnomics/posts/1041529282885976?__tn__=K-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKnomics%2Fposts%2F1041529282885976%3F__tn__%3DK-R&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=b9bb5dc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKnomics/posts/1041529282885976?__tn__=K-R</a>"},{"pid":"7bd302bc8fce3fdf845939db1f2566a66d00fcf6","tid":1863979,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"【TVB推優惠未能阻止客戶流失 出糧每月燒1.3億 邁入最後倒數？】<br />\n<br />\n業界指TVB今年農曆新年檔期廣告收費較去年減低一半吸客，惟仍有超過三成客戶轉向其他電視頻道。<br />\n<br />\n有廣告業內人士指，現時很多公司都會留意網上及Facebook群組的意見，更有客戶收到投訴電話要求取消在TVB落廣告，令不少品牌因而打退堂鼓，最新有金鳳香米代理行之一的聚大行和發聲明將盡快處理的津路烏龍茶等。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士續指，TVB過去會按個別客戶上一個年度的廣告預算或承諾開支提供不同優惠，但普遍均會要求廣告客戶新一年加碼，因此較難評估TVB在過去半年的廣告價錢減幅，但在今年農曆新年黃金時段檔期，TVB向客戶提供減價優惠，實質上只需要繳付去年農曆新年的一半費用便可，他形容減幅誇張。<br />\n<br />\n事實上翻查過去一年電視廣播的年報及半年報告，TVB 2018全年及2019半年收入分別為44.77億元及19.65億元，當中廣告客戶收入佔比最多，分別為24.4億元及11.36億元，均佔逾半。至2018年底TVB共有4,041名全職員工。2018全年工資及薪酬為15.9億元，即每月平均工資為32,793元（相信因藝人及高層薪金拉高）。<br />\n<br />\n至去年6月底，TVB現金及現金等價物為6.83億元，按年大減43.5%，而因早前發債，最少仍有1.36億元利息需要兩年內支付。<br />\n<br />\n不知TVB還有沒有機會反底呢?<br />\n<br />\n#TVB #客戶流失 #電視廣播 #廣告<br />\n<br />\n去年中剩7億現金 僅出糧每月燒1.3億 邁入最後倒數？<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3bblYtw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bblYtw&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=9722c7ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3bblYtw</a><br />\n<br />\n農曆新年廣告收費減半 TVB推優惠未能阻止客戶流失<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uWTq6B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uWTq6B&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=2273ee32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uWTq6B</a>"},{"pid":"01a94efab289775bfbb6ee8762f95c6b1c00e6b1","tid":1863979,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"大家可以再加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗佢廣告商/偽人/新聞部賤畜板<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dae75e6ba07ddf8a20fbab137a59ff81684371","tid":1863979,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d135f83114779602d38d5ce43461b9ffd6129cf5","tid":1863979,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"大家幫手行多步宣傳下比你ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n聯署要求世衛主席辭職<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funited-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=56353e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general</a><br />\n<br />\n美孚手足被爆頭要推上 twitter<br />\